# 🚲 LA Metro BikeShare Analysis

## 📌 Project Overview

The **LA Metro BikeShare Analysis Project** focuses on evaluating **bike station performance, trip patterns, and multimodal transportation integration**. The goal is to provide **data-driven recommendations** for improving station placement, increasing ridership, and optimizing infrastructure within **Downtown LA and the Westside regions**.

This project uses **geospatial analysis, predictive modeling, and transit data integration** to enhance bike share accessibility and efficiency. The insights generated will support **infrastructure planning, multimodal transportation strategies, and investment decisions** for Metro BikeShare.

